1
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,439
It's so dangerous.

2
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,930
Why did you go alone?

3
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,600
This is just a scratch.

4
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:40,930
I just didn't expect

5
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:43,040
that foreigners would actually

6
00:00:43,040 --> 00:00:45,700
grow poppies on the land Song Huainan sold them.

7
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:48,000
Aren't they using opium

8
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:50,200
to harm our people?

9
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,520
The land contract

10
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:53,800
I stole from Johnson earlier

11
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:55,280
will come in handy now.

12
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:57,500
It has Song Huainan's signature.

13
00:00:59,000 --> 00:00:59,840
Tomorrow,

14
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:02,570
I'll go to the Song house and get the contract.

15
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:04,040
The evidence is solid this time.

16
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,200
It's enough to bring down Song Huainan.

17
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:07,000
Let me go get the contract.

18
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,360
It's too dangerous for you.

19
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:09,800
I'm a Song, after all.

20
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,360
I can come and go freely.

21
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:12,160
No way.

22
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:14,039
You're a thorn in his side now.

23
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:16,640
Going there would be walking right into a trap.

24
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:22,120
Okay.

25
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,400
I'll do as you say.

26
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:26,800
All done.

27
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:37,680
Does it hurt?

28
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,560
No.

29
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:40,200
Come here.

30
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,720
Don't go alone again.

31
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,440
I promise.

32
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,520
Commander.

33
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,890
Pass on the order. Search the whole city for Zhu Luoli

34
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,560
and Song Qingzhou.

35
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,120
I must find him tonight.

36
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,760
Yes, sir.

37
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:34,290
Commander, Mr. Johnson is here to see you.

38
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,000
He says he has something important

39
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,130
to discuss with you.

40
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,079
Someone broke into my plantation tonight.

41
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,640
You must catch that person immediately.

42
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,880
You're so anxious over such a small matter?

43
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:51,360
I don't have time for this.

44
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:53,560
I won't hide it from you anymore.

45
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:56,120
I planted poppies all over that plantation.

46
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:58,040
If word gets out,

47
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,480
we'll both go down.

48
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,160
You grew poppies?

49
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:05,200
Do you know that's a capital offense?

50
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,840
Even an ambassador can't save you.

51
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,370
You did this behind my back.

52
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,680
I'll shoot you right now.

53
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,840
Even if you kill me now,

54
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,240
you're still on the hook.

55
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,280
Are you threatening me?

56
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,120
I advise you

57
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,160
to think this through calmly.

58
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,760
Killing me won't do you any good.

59
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:32,290
Don't you want the most advanced arms?

60
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,480
I can get them.

61
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:35,120
Just help me settle this.

62
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:48,160
Opium must not be sold to our people.

63
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,880
Okay, no problem.

64
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,800
Get out.

65
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,560
Get out before I change my mind.

66
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,000
By the way,

67
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:00,680
the one who broke into my plantation

68
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,080
seems to be your brother.

69
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,640
Song Qingzhou.

70
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,520
It's you again.

71
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,920
Commander, we found Zhu Luoli.

72
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,580
She is with the Young Marshal.

73
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,600
My dear brother

74
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:42,159
actually betrayed me for a woman.

75
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:50,920
The one I've protected since childhood

76
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,400
has stabbed me in the back.

77
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:57,640
Very well.

78
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,400
In that case,

79
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,610
don't blame me for being ruthless.

80
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,920
What do we do next?

81
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:10,080
Keep an eye on those two.

82
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:11,080
Yes, sir.

83
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,080
Zhu Luoli,

84
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:23,240
you went to such lengths to set up this grand scheme for me.

85
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,490
Killing you straight away,

86
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:29,200
wouldn't that be a waste?

87
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,680
I will make you

88
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,000
suffer endlessly.

89
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,400
Luoli.

90
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,640
Let's go. Come back with me.

91
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,440
Where to?

92
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,520
Luoli.

93
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:37,400
Song Huainan has set an ambush at the Song residence.

94
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,520
Going back with me to get the contract now

95
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,440
is just too dangerous.

96
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,680
Aren't you in danger too?

97
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,080
Song Huainan already considers you

98
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,120
his enemy.

99
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,240
If he discovers you,

100
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,240
do you think he'll let you go easily?

101
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,880
I'm skilled in martial arts.

102
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:50,520
Besides, I know the Song residence well.

103
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,360
Even if it's dangerous,

104
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,440
I can escape.

105
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,880
Trust me, okay?

106
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,720
You don't know where the contract is hidden.

107
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,280
I'll go.

108
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,640
You just need to ensure all this final evidence

109
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,280
is handed over to the Governor.

110
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:05,210
I can't let you take any more risks.

111
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:15,320
Luoli.

112
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:18,960
For so long,

113
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,560
you've endured too much on your own.

114
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,720
I can't let you be in any more danger.

115
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,640
Qingzhou.

116
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:34,370
Thank you for appearing in my life.

117
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,960
Making me feel like I'm not alone,

118
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:42,320
facing all of this by myself.
